    <!-- Intro Section -->
    <section id="intro">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                    <h2 class="section-heading">What is Save With Me?</h2>
                    <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">Save With Me is an integrated platform for mobilizing members of a community around the shared goal of resource conservation. <br><br> Users can create their own shopping lists and join those of others in their area to exploit the power of bulk buying.<br> </h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row text-center">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                        <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-money fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                    </span>
                    <h4 class="intro-heading">Saving You Money</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">By allowing users to pool together resources to buy products in bulk, Save With Me helps individuals access wholesale prices as a cost-saving alternative to buying smaller quantities, which are often more costly per unit. This not only reduces the cost of commonly-needed products, but it also increases the accessibility of products that may otherwise be unattainable.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                        <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-clock-o fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                    </span>
                    <h4 class="intro-heading">Saving You Time</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">Through the in-app communication system and optional secure payment service, members of a finalized listing can coordinate on the logistics for completing their purchase. Post-purchase analytics will log each user's experience, allowing them to crowdsource future recommendations, contribute to the existing database of local bulk deals, and visualize their overall savings.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                        <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-shopping-cart fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                    </span>
                    <h4 class="intro-heading">Saving You Effort</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">While empowering users to take advantage of the money-saving quality of bulk purchasing, Save With Me simultaneously provides an avenue to circumvent other issues blocking access to products. Coordination on payment and purchasing, for instance, creates potential solutions to impasses such as transportation limitations, lack of time, or unawareness of bulk deals.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

